OOC:( Scratch the last post of Darkmouse.  My emails came in out of 
order and I couldn't get to the message board for a little while.  I 
appologize for any confusion.)

::DarkMouse::

She flew across the room and hit the wall.  she fell to the floor 
with a thud.  Shaking her head, she looked at Megatron holding up 
Dracona.  "Commander, the drug will take effect in a moment and she 
will talk freely to you."  She rubbed the back of her head.  That 
last blow hurt, a lot.  She went out of the room and looked at 
Scorponok.  

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Talon Harvilicz" <wilddance_mare@h...> 
wrote:
> Megatron:
> 
> 
> Megatron stepped to Dark Mouse and back-handed her again. "I will 
be the one 
> to ask the questions, vermin!" he snarled at her. He turned his 
cold eyes to 
> Dracona. He took a step closer to her and took the straps off of 
her. But 
> before she could make any attempt to escape, he grabbed her by the 
throat 
> and swung her around. He had her several feet off of the ground.
> 
> "Now, we shall talk, yes." he said to Dracona. "What were you doing 
here?" 
> He squeezed a little tighter around her neck. "And what is your 
concern for 
> the devise?"
